channel.title: Need a good programer either temp or permanent
channel.description:
Today at 01:39:17 PM I have self taught my self how to code/progrAm as far as i could get on my own i specialize more in ownership and web design my sel which is why i need a good coder to help code and maintain my server this code/program position will mostly be done thru teamviewer on my pc so i can learn while you work if that is ok with you! If not pm me a different solution. My server at the moment is not on a paid website or a paid online server. What i am doing since i have played literally 100's of different servers and seen all the good and bad and i am tryin to put all the good ive seen into my server i had already coded alot and fixed alot my self and have a webclient on my personal website i havent registered it yet because there are still some things that need fixxed that i cannot figure out. I have more details if your interested pm me on here or add me on skype Skype user: Steven.Clark73 Columbus, ohio. Usa I will not be online for about 3-4 hours from the time i made this post Hoping i find someone even if your just wanting to help temporarily you do not have to stay if you do not want too but i preffer a full time coder:)
The client/source is a 317 (forgot to mention)
Thanks for your time!!!

Pretty much exactly what I told this kid:

moparisthebest.com
